casebody.data:
No. 564. Jennie L. Graves et al., Petitioners, v. Anna P. Ashburn, Executrix, etc., et al. January 20, 1908. Mr. Marion Erwin and Mr. W. J. Wallace for petitioners. No appearance for respondents.

Petition for a writ of certiorari to the United States Circuit Court of Appeals for the Fifth Circuit granted.
